WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.334 --> 00:00:06.467
man: It is easy to follow
a blog on Blogger.

00:00:06.467 --> 00:00:08.968
Click on the Follow button.

00:00:08.968 --> 00:00:12.000
Choose the account
you want to use.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:18.467
Then sign in
with your credential.

00:00:18.467 --> 00:00:21.234
Choose whether to follow
publicly

00:00:21.234 --> 00:00:22.968
or privately.

00:00:22.968 --> 00:00:26.734
Then click "Follow this blog."

00:00:26.734 --> 00:00:30.434
And you're done.

00:00:30.434 --> 00:00:33.834
View your profile
to see this blog listed

00:00:33.834 --> 00:00:36.100
with the other sites
you've joined.

